=== 早年 ===
{{expand section}}

=== 職業生涯 ===
;多倫多藍鳥
2009年3月30日，藍鳥總教練{{link-en|斯圖·蓋斯頓|Cito Gaston}}宣布羅梅洛將在接下來的賽季加入先發投手的陣容中，此前羅梅洛在春訓對[[休士頓太空人|休士頓太空人]]繳出7局的好投<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.thestar.com/Sports/article/610784|title=Romero cracks Jays' rotation|last=Campbell|first=Morgan|date=2009-03-31|work=Toronto Star|access-date=2010-06-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5qSz9bJnH?url=http://www.thestar.com/Sports/article/610784|archive-date=2010-06-13}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/sports/baseball/story/2009/03/30/sp-jays-romero.html|title=Romero wins spot in Blue Jays rotation|date=2009-03-30|work=CBC.ca|publisher=Canadian Broadcasting Corporation|access-date=2010-06-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5qT09S7zA?url=http://www.cbc.ca/sports/baseball/story/2009/03/30/sp-jays-romero.html|archive-date=2010-06-13}}</ref>。4月9日是他的大聯盟初登板，對手是[[底特律老虎|底特律老虎]]，羅梅洛以6局失2分的表現獲得生涯首勝<ref>[http://us.lrd.yahoo.com/_ylt=Ag7URYhnBoGaOP6Pewjyvj9G2vAI;_ylu=X3oDMTFnOTdxcGVjBGlpZAMxMTgxOTU4MTM4NjcwNTMyNjEwOARub2gDNQRwb3MDMQRyaWQDODI3NDg0Mg--/SIG=12mtgchkl/**http://www.mlive.com/tigers/index.ssf/2009/04/tigers_porcello_loses_debut_to.html Tigers' Rick Porcello loses debut to Toronto]</ref>{{NoteTag|與他同場對陣的老虎投手是滾地球投手[[瑞克·波瑟羅|瑞克·波瑟羅]]。值得一提的是，這場比賽是大聯盟史上頭一次有兩位首輪選秀的球員（投手）在彼此的首秀相遭遇<ref>[https://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/recap?gid=290408114 Cabrera homers twice as Tigers beat Blue Jays 5–1] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304132043/https://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/recap?gid=290408114 |date=2016-03-04 }}</ref>。}}。包括這場比賽在內，他在生涯的前三次先發拿下2勝0負的成績，期間防禦率是出色的1.71。4月20日，他因為打噴嚏過猛而拉傷右頸，進入傷兵名單<ref>[http://www.canada.com/sports/tennis/Jays+Romero+Ryan+disabled+list/1527489/story.html Canada.com]</ref>，直到5月底才重返大聯盟賽場<ref>''Gaston faces big decisions on rotation'', by Robert MacLeod, ''The Globe and Mail'', 2009-04-30, p. S2.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=4199609|title=Toronto Blue Jays call up Casey Janssen, Joe Inglett, Ricky Romero|date=2009-05-22|work=ESPN|access-date=2010-06-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5qT2OUL0t?url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=4199609|archive-date=2010-06-14|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。在明星賽之前，羅梅洛的表現傑出，接連擊敗衛冕冠軍[[費城費城人|費城費城人]]（6月26日<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fan590.com/news/sports/more.jsp?content=s261521320|title=Romero pitches seven-inning two-hitter as Blue Jays beat Phillies again, 6–1|last=Millson|first=Larry|date=2009-06-26|work=The Fan 590|access-date=2010-06-14}</ref>）、美聯冠軍[[坦帕灣光芒|坦帕灣光芒]]（7月1日<ref>{{cite news|url=https://nationalpost.com/sports/story.html?id=1749632|title=Romero pitches gem to salvage series against Rays|last=Lott|first=John|date=2009-07-01|work=National Post|access-date=2010-06-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5qT3J7SSf?url=http://www.nationalpost.com/sports/story.html?id=1749632|archive-date=2010-06-14|deadurl=yes}}</ref>），以及同分區強權[[紐約洋基|紐約洋基]]（7月6日<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/07/sports/baseball/07yankees.html?_r=1|title=Umpires and Rookie Pitcher Baffle Jeter and the Yankees|last=Curry|first=Jack|date=2009-07-07|work=The New York Times|page=10|access-date=2010-06-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5qT3aPRFy?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/07/sports/baseball/07yankees.html?_r=1|archive-date=2010-06-14|deadurl=yes}}</ref>）等隊伍，期間並有連續24局未失分的演出（平隊史菜鳥球員紀錄）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/31767011/ns/sports-baseball/|title=Yankees' rally falls short, just miss Jays sweep|date=2009-07-06|work=MSNBC|access-date=2010-06-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5qTAVJlFZ?url=http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/31767011/ns/sports-baseball/|archive-date=2010-06-14}}</ref>，是球隊實際上的二號先發，也使他成為新人王獎項的有力競爭者{{NoteTag|其他表現精采的菜鳥球員還包括了[[芝加哥白襪|白襪]]內野手{{link-en|戈登·貝克漢|Gordon Beckham}}，白襪內野手{{link-en|傑森·尼克斯|Jayson Nix}}，以及老虎先發[[瑞克·波瑟羅|瑞克·波瑟羅]]。}}。

羅梅洛在翌（2010年）年開季率先刷新個人單場奪三振紀錄（12次，4月13日），此外也完成個人首次完投（5月15日）。2011年6月26日，他在跨聯盟賽事中打出個人生涯首安，投球方面則有完投完封勝的演出，率領球隊橫掃對手[[聖路易紅雀|聖路易紅雀]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Overbey |first=Steve |url=http://toronto.bluejays.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2011_06_26_tormlb_slnmlb_1&mode=recap&c_id=tor |title=MLB.com Gameday | bluejays.com: Gameday |publisher=Toronto.bluejays.mlb.com |date=2011-06-26 |access-date=2013-03-26 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304053655/http://toronto.bluejays.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2011_06_26_tormlb_slnmlb_1&mode=recap&c_id=tor |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{NoteTag|羅梅洛的隊友在這場比賽中共攻下5分，對他而言是難得的火力支援。在這之前，藍鳥已連續八次在他先發的比賽中得分不超過2分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://toronto.bluejays.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20110620&content_id=20772698&vkey=news_tor&fext=.jsp&c_id=tor |title=Ricky Romero solid, but one mistake sinks Blue Jays in shutout loss to Braves | bluejays.com: News |publisher=Toronto.bluejays.mlb.com |access-date=2013-03-26}}</ref>。}}。7月10日，他替補[[波士頓紅襪|紅襪]]投手[[乔恩·莱斯特|乔恩·莱斯特]]參加[[2011年美國職棒大聯盟全明星賽|全明星賽]]{{NoteTag|莱斯特則是替補[[西雅圖水手|水手]]投手[[費利克斯·赫南德茲|費利克斯·赫南德茲]]參賽，後者因為在明星賽前先發登板，而讓出資格。}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20110710&content_id=21708972&vkey=pr_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |title=Jon Lester, Ricky Romero named American League All-Stars | MLB.com: Official Info |publisher=Mlb.mlb.com |date=2013-03-12 |access-date=2013-03-26 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304024001/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20110710&content_id=21708972&vkey=pr_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年賽季，羅梅洛榮膺開幕戰先發。8月第一週，羅梅洛獲選為美聯單週最佳球員，進而以5勝0負的表現獲選8月的美聯最佳投手，期間的防禦率（2.05）、對手打擊率（.160）皆領先大聯盟<ref>[http://tsn.ca/mlb/story/?id=375271 Blue Jays' Romero named Pitcher of the Month] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013122333/http://tsn.ca/mlb/story/?id=375271 |date=2012-10-13 }}</ref>。

2012年4月15日，儼然已是藍鳥王牌的羅梅洛再次在球季開幕戰（4月5日）登板<ref>[http://toronto.bluejays.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120401&content_id=27823160&vkey=news_tor&c_id=tor Ricky Romero wants to lead Blue Jays by example] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130419032015/http://toronto.bluejays.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120401&content_id=27823160&vkey=news_tor&c_id=tor |date=2013-04-19 }}</ref>，並在下一場先發取得個人生涯第500次奪三振。以上半季的成績來看，羅梅洛的8勝1負記錄看似不差，但他的防禦率是令人擔憂的4.34。下半季他的表現則判若兩人，在球季剩餘的17次先發中，他僅有1勝13負的戰績，防禦率暴漲到7.35，在身體沒有明顯傷勢的前提下，羅梅洛的偏差表現引起了專家的注意。直到球季結束後，他才承認自己隱瞞了膝部傷勢<ref name=vice>{{cite news |last1=Murphy |first1=Blake |title=Ricky Romero Is Determined to Make an Improbable Comeback to the Majors |url=https://www.vice.com/en_ca/article/qvw8zv/ricky-romero-is-determined-to-make-an-improbable-comeback-to-the-majors |access-date=2020-01-12 |work=Vice Sports |date=2017-12-19 |language=en |archive-date=2020-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811223814/https://www.vice.com/en_ca/article/qvw8zv/ricky-romero-is-determined-to-make-an-improbable-comeback-to-the-majors |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年2月5日，總教練{{link-en|約翰·吉本斯|John Gibbons}}宣布，羅梅洛將擔任球隊的五號先發。不過，隨著羅梅洛在春訓的不穩定表現，他在開季被下放到小聯盟1A<ref name=Dunedin>{{cite web|title=BLUE JAYS OPTION ROMERO TO SINGLE-A DUNEDIN|url=https://www.tsn.ca/mlb/story/?id=419178|publisher=TSN.ca|access-date=2013-03-26|date=2013-03-26|archive-date=2013-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130629185432/http://www.tsn.ca/mlb/story/?id=419178|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在球季一開始便因傷所苦，傷勢似乎影響了他的投球機制<ref name=vice/>。5月3日，羅梅洛結束了延長春訓，重返大聯盟。在接下來的兩次先發機會當中，他繳出0勝2負、防禦率12.46的成績。5月9日，再次遭下放<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130509&content_id=47052952&vkey=news_tor&c_id=tor|title=Romero optioned to Triple-A after rough start|last=Meisel|first=Zack|work=MLB.com|date=2013-05-09|access-date=2013-05-09|archive-date=2013-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214223310/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130509&content_id=47052952&vkey=news_tor&c_id=tor|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.nationalpost.com/2013/05/09/blue-jays-option-ricky-romero-to-buffalo/|title=Blue Jays option Ricky Romero to Buffalo|date=2013-05-09|access-date=2013-05-09|first=Joh|last=Lott}}</ref>。6月1日，被移出40人名單<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130601&content_id=49290930&vkey=news_tor&c_id=tor|title=Morrow lands on DL with forearm strain|last=Berry|first=Adam|work=MLB.com|date=2013-06-01|access-date=2013-06-01|archive-date=2014-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140319174850/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130601&content_id=49290930&vkey=news_tor&c_id=tor|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在小聯盟3A度過剩餘賽季。9月3日，羅梅洛透過名單擴編再次回到大聯盟，剩餘的賽季期間，僅以後援身分出賽兩場，亦是他在大聯盟最後的登場紀錄。

;2014年之後
2014年，藍鳥雖邀請他參與春訓，但他未能躋身大聯盟陣容<ref>{{cite web|url=http://jaysjournal.com/2014/03/19/ricky-romero-marcus-stroman-assigned-toronto-blue-jays-minor-league-camp-rumors-news-roster-moves/|title=Romero, Stroman assigned to Toronto Blue Jays' minor league camp|last=Wray|first=Michael|work=jaysjournal.com|date=2014-03-19|access-date=2014-03-19|archive-date=2017-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117070032/https://jaysjournal.com/2014/03/19/ricky-romero-marcus-stroman-assigned-toronto-blue-jays-minor-league-camp-rumors-news-roster-moves/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月，羅梅洛進行了膝蓋手術，使他直到2015年季初仍無法正常出賽。2015年4月25日，藍鳥球團正式釋出了羅梅洛<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/blue-jays-release-pitcher-ricky-romero/|title=Blue Jays release pitcher Ricky Romero|last=Galindo|first=Peter|work=Sportsnet|date=2015-04-25|access-date=2015-04-25|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108181037/https://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/blue-jays-release-pitcher-ricky-romero/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他轉而與[[舊金山巨人|舊金山巨人]]簽下小聯盟合約<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thestar.com/sports/baseball/2015/05/11/san-francisco-giants-sign-ricky-romero-to-minor-league-deal.html|title=San Francisco Giants sign Ricky Romero to minor-league deal|work=thestar.com|date=2015-05-11|access-date=2015-05-12|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812071133/https://www.thestar.com/sports/baseball/2015/05/11/san-francisco-giants-sign-ricky-romero-to-minor-league-deal.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而在接下來的兩年期間，羅梅洛仍沒有找回身手。迫於他的狀況，巨人球團在2017年4月29日將他釋出<ref name=BRM>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.cgi?id=romero001ric|title=Ricky Romero Register Statistics & History|work=Baseball-Reference|access-date=2017-04-30|archive-date=2016-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160622010501/http://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.cgi?id=romero001ric|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2017/04/minor-mlb-transactions-42917.html|title=Minor MLB Transactions: 4/29/17|last=Byrne|first=Connor|work=mlbtraderumors.com|date=2017-04-29|access-date=2017-04-30|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112011844/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2017/04/minor-mlb-transactions-42917.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年5月30日，羅梅洛和[[墨西哥棒球聯盟|墨西哥聯盟]]的{{link-en|蒂華納公牛|Toros de Tijuana}}簽約<ref>{{cite web|url=https://jaysjournal.com/2017/05/30/blue-jays-ricky-romero-signs-mexican-league-team/|title=Blue Jays: Ricky Romero signs with Mexican League team|last=Richer|first=Clayton|work=jaysjournal.com|date=2017-05-30|access-date=2017-05-31|archive-date=2017-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171002115352/https://jaysjournal.com/2017/05/30/blue-jays-ricky-romero-signs-mexican-league-team/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他為公牛後援出賽12場，在15局的投球中，平均防禦率為5.40。8月初，他的身分轉為非活躍，不再代表球隊出賽，合約則仍然有效。

2017年8月之後，羅梅洛便未在任何聯盟有出賽紀錄。2018年12月31日，他透過個人的Instagram帳戶宣布退休<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BsEjNsxh8XN/|title=Ricky Romero on Instagram}}</ref>。

== 技術特點 ==
羅梅洛的二縫線速球球速在87至92英哩間，四縫線速球球速則在92至95英哩間。他的變化球種則有變速球、區球和滑球等<ref>{{cite web|url=http://60ft6in.com/al-east/toronto-blue-jays/ |title=Pitcher Scouting Reports » Toronto Blue Jays |publisher=60ft6in |date=2011-07-07 |access-date=2013-03-26 |deadurl=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017124702/http://60ft6in.com/al-east/toronto-blue-jays/ |archive-date=2012-10-17 }}</ref>。

== 個人生活 ==
羅梅洛有一個弟弟（加布里埃爾Gabriel{{NoteTag|加布里埃爾亦是一名投手，藍鳥曾在業餘選秀中選擇他<ref>[http://toronto.bluejays.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100609&content_id=10996034&notebook_id=10999792&vkey=notebook_tor&fext=.jsp&c_id=tor Jays draft Romero's brother] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140725204411/http://toronto.bluejays.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100609&content_id=10996034&notebook_id=10999792&vkey=notebook_tor&fext=.jsp&c_id=tor |date=2014-07-25 }} MLB.com. Accessed on 2013-02-17.</ref>。}}）、兩個妹妹<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120509&content_id=30831242&vkey=news_tor&c_id=tor|title=Mother's Day comes early for the Romeros|last=Chisholm|first=Gregor|work=MLB.com|date=2012-05-11|access-date=2014-04-22|archive-date=2014-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140725203116/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120509&content_id=30831242&vkey=news_tor&c_id=tor|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他與加拿大足球選手[[卡拉·兰|卡拉·兰]]育有二子<ref name=Davidi>{{citation
